OL,3,CTeenager appears in court after man in
OL,4,Chis 60s stabbed on golf course
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder after a man in his
OL,9,F60s was stabbed in Stafford.
OL,11,FThe incident happened shortly before
OL,12,F7pm on 15 May on a public footpath
OL,13,Frunning through Stafford golf course.
OL,15,FThe victim was found by a member of
OL,16,Fthe public on a bench and taken to
OL,17,Fhospital where he remains in a serious
OL,18,Fbut stable condition.
